    <!--~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ Temperature Forecast Window [TFW] ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~-->
        <!-- This window is visible when a tile is picked on the world map and you click on the Forecast button in the
        temperature tab.

        side note to translators:
        Each column has a header string and an associated tool-tip (shown on mouse-over the column).Be wary that the
        column width on that window is very small! (I'd say at most 8 or 9 chars without friggin' up the whole window
        layout.)

        In case you need it: RimWorld units of time are as follow:

        1 tick = 1/60 second (note: a "real" second)
        1 hour = 2500 ticks
        1 day = 24 hours
        5 days = 1 twelfth
        3 twelves = 1 season (quadrum)
        4 quadrum = 1 year
        -->

